---
title: Japanese Beef & Garlic Rice Bowl with Quick-Pickled Onion & Coconut-Chilli Mayo
description: Add tons of flavour to beef with a tasty sauce mixture, then fill a bowl with garlicky jasmine rice, add the beef and loads of
veggies and top it all off with pickled onion, crispy shallots and a sensational mayo. This is a recipe for a meal you won't forget!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/japanese-beef-bowl-30f649dd.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/japanese-beef-bowl-617256621a35d826ab16a08a-5888196f.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/japanese-beef-and-garlic-rice-bowl-617256621a35d826ab16a08a
